      "content": "it's exactly like that. a void. sometimes i just sit on the floor and stare at the wall for hours because moving feels like such a waste of energy. everything feels so heavy and pointless. like i'm just a ghost haunting a house that doesn't belong to me anymore. does it ever actually get better? or are we just supposed to endure this emptiness forever?",
